Class Stream.Empty<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • javaslang.collection.Stream.Empty<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Component type of the Stream.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Iterable<T>, IntFunction<T>, LinearSeq<T>, Seq<T>, Stream<T>, Traversable<T>, TraversableOnce<T>, Value<T>
    Enclosing interface:
    Stream<T>

    public static final class Stream.Empty<T>
extends Object
implements Stream<T>, Serializable
    The empty Stream.

    This is a singleton, i.e. not Cloneable.
